{"tid":2343422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"太妍在IG曬「梗圖」回應戀愛傳聞！在網路上引發熱議，網友：「King太妍！很有Sense」","createTime":"2020-12-28T02:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T03:53:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2af7996eba84485610b899177d97a24a94dd11","tid":2343422,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_f98945d80b129ad2f1545c28d3fd9eb6/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-27/132610-890728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_f98945d80b129ad2f1545c28d3fd9eb6%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-27%2F132610-890728.jpg&h=f47a0767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n27日，韓媒news24曝：「太妍、Ravi已經戀愛一年，兩人前經過朋友的介紹相識，確認彼此的心意，在聖誕節期間也往返於對方家中約會。」之後，兩人的所屬社SM、GROOVL1N也反駁：「兩人只是關係親近的前後輩，戀愛不是事實。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b9c6d809d235a545a94d596954c95ead/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-27/132610-890727.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b9c6d809d235a545a94d596954c95ead%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-27%2F132610-890727.jpg&h=7d0bace9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當天，太妍也在IG限時動態上傳Key的梗圖，上面的文字是：「忍耐很久的有用的表情包。」似乎是透露對戀愛消息感到荒唐，這讓不少網友表示：「太霸氣了」、「姊姊真的太有趣」、「King太妍」、「太妍就是超爽快 哈哈哈哈」、「為什麼這麼可愛呀」、「比誰都信任的解釋」、「太妍就是汽水啊（很爽快的意思）」、「太好笑了，很有Sense」等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e930109ffa46ed58284e3873a465ab23/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-27/132610-890725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e930109ffa46ed58284e3873a465ab23%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-27%2F132610-890725.jpg&h=0ac0c033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過...這天真的有一個好消息！就是太妍以《What Do I Call You》在《人氣歌謠》獲得初一位，即使沒有進行打歌，成績也非常好，粗卡粗卡！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8a3f38d841786ec42988a68ff846fcbc/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-27/132610-890726.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8a3f38d841786ec42988a68ff846fcbc%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-27%2F132610-890726.jpg&h=fcdd43ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b0e983efead488ee9448e1003ea626b1789f6db","tid":2343422,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T02:44:11.000Z","msg":"@牙邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed4f26097f3db67c80315a1bae03989b339a884","tid":2343422,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b0e983efead488ee9448e1003ea626b1789f6db","tid":2343422,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T02:44:11.000Z","msg":"@牙邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"已失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c42af9cfc23726a057edee3cb81d4e6a6a0d01","tid":2343422,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T02:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fd54bf7c39a50cb97b9e480950cf208b420856","tid":2343422,"uid":3405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"金泰妍世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ee2e6c6821d414ff681b88c0ac1fabbf6c122a","tid":2343422,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T02:56:42.000Z","msg":"想戀愛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0992ffd5299ca07c450a63689df76e8409381815","tid":2343422,"uid":16659